						<div class="postbody">So I've finally finished my first goal: Make something that moves in all directions. I would like to know if any of my code would be deemed wrong or unsafe to work on a proper NES, or if anything is working improperly. I've tested it on FCEUX and it runs super smooth, but Nintendulator seems to be a bit choppy. 
<br />
<br />Question:
<br />   Does the AND command change the contents of the accumulator? I had to put a LDA command for every button because it wouldn't read anything past A when I didn't.
<br />
<br />Any advice would be appreciated, thanks!
<br />
